title: Drawing, "Foliate Design"
description: Sets of delicate curved leaves branch off from a central vertical stem on the left and right. Small berries, close to the stem, are interspersed. The single color green appears to have faded from the original.

tombstone.epitaph:
Drawing, "Foliate Design".
28 x 21.5 cm (11 x 8 1/2 in.). Gift of Ellen Gustav Jensen. 1956-47-17.
